title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Oct 28 2021

description:
Drama on Capitol Hill: Biden agenda on the brink. Buck out sick today. President Trump joins Clay and Buck on Friday. The details of the reconciliation bill as we know it. Florida Surgeon General Ladapo speaks truth to power. Floyd Mayweather under attack for supporting Kyrie Irving's vaccine stance.
